<br />
1 - Combat:  during combat, these little white arrows show up above and to the left/right of my target.  It seems as though the more arrows are on one side, the less chance I have of hitting from that side.  Is that right?  Also, I see yellowish green arrows from time to time as well - are those showing where I am vulnerable?  or what?<br />
<br />
